Name: cpplint
Version: 1.3.0
Summary: An automated checker to make sure a C++ file follows Google's C++ style guide
Home-page: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cpplint
Maintainer: Andrew Davis
Maintainer-email: see_github@nospam.com
